&lt;p&gt;This is a founding leadership seat with an existing, meaningful team underneath it. Not a greenfield gamble, and not a maintenance job. You get a real mandate from day one and the latitude to shape a hub from the ground up, at Head of Engineering seniority, reporting directly to the VP of Engineering. You start as the team&#39;s line leader, but you won&#39;t stay one unless you choose to: as the hub gr

